In the wake of a four-month cyber-assault by Chinese hackers on the , during which multiple high-level  reporters’ passwords were stolen using sophisticated infiltration techniques,  would like to once again affirm our commitment to providing the Chinese government with our employees’ passwords and personal information with total and unquestioning cooperation.As a billion-dollar multinational conglomerate and fellow global superpower,  shares a special affinity with the guiding principles of The People’s Republic of China.